c: 3
v: 97
t: "Mukari omo khulimwo nende ebimanyisio bilolekha, amemelo ka Ibraheem, ne winjilamwo abanende omulembe, Ne neshilachilo shia Nyasaye khubandu okhuhija khu- inzu eyo, khu ulia unyala oluchendo lwokhutsia eyo. Ne ulia ukhaya ne Nyasaye toto shiyenya shiosi shiosi khubandu tawe (nomuyinda)"